1005
00:55:10,542 --> 00:55:11,714
Don't worry.

1006
00:55:11,708 --> 00:55:13,585
I can make anything!

1007
00:55:21,208 --> 00:55:23,381
Uncle, this is for you.

1008
00:55:24,542 --> 00:55:25,384
