1014
00:55:38,333 --> 00:55:39,084
Fﬂends?

1015
00:55:40,417 --> 00:55:41,714
Then you must be

1016
00:55:42,000 --> 00:55:43,343
such good friends

1017
00:55:43,333 --> 00:55:44,801
