1021
00:55:56,167 --> 00:55:57,259
It's for your own good!

1022
00:55:57,708 --> 00:55:58,755
Uncle,

1023
00:55:59,083 --> 00:56:00,551
don't assume everyone

1024
00:56:00,542 --> 00:56:01,384
