1088
01:00:13,250 --> 01:00:14,502
and talk to it.

1089
01:00:15,125 --> 01:00:17,002
Wow, it's magic!

1090
01:00:18,333 --> 01:00:19,380
Then...

1091
01:00:20,542 --> 01:00:22,340
